{"id":537387,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2016/08/无辜推友被躺枪后，霍顿父亲向同名同姓者道歉/","date":"2016-08-10T06:39:12Z","modified":"2016-08-10T06:39:12Z","title":"无辜推友被躺枪后，霍顿父亲向同名同姓者道歉","content":"<p>孙杨近日被澳洲游泳选手霍顿公开称为“嗑药的骗子”后，大量“爱国青年”<del>再度</del>翻墙<a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/tag/%e5%b0%8f%e7%b2%89%e7%ba%a2%e7%bf%bb%e5%a2%99%e4%bd%9c%e6%88%98/\" target=\"_blank\">出征</a>，对霍顿的社交账号进行狂轰滥炸，并要求他为此道歉。但后被媒体曝出，许多“出征”者显然误将一位名为 Mark Horton (@_markhorton) 的英国人当作了澳洲选手 Mack Horton (@_mackhorton)，找错了围攻对象。</p>\n<p>这位莫名躺枪的英国人反应过来后，<strong>当天即发布了置顶<a href=\"https://twitter.com/_markhorton/status/762187550970810369\" target=\"_blank\">推文</a>，声明自己不是那位澳洲游泳选手</strong>：</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/markhorton-e1470806365914.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-537389\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/markhorton-e1470806365914.jpg\" width=\"450\" height=\"245\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/markhorton-e1470806365914.jpg 1926w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/markhorton-e1470806365914-300x163.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/markhorton-e1470806365914-768x417.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/markhorton-e1470806365914-1024x557.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>我必须得说，我不是那名评价了中国泳将的澳洲运动员</p></blockquote>\n<p>虽然也有中国新媒体帐号<a href=\"http://chuansong.me/n/496023942960\" target=\"_blank\">报道了</a>这出乌龙，<strong>然而这好像并没有用</strong>。8月8日，英国人 Mark 发推称自己过去<strong>两天内被@了超20万次</strong>：</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/markhorton3.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-537390\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/markhorton3.jpg\" alt=\"markhorton3\" width=\"450\" height=\"106\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/markhorton3.jpg 1798w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/markhorton3-300x71.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/markhorton3-768x181.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/markhorton3-1024x241.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>过去两天里被@超过20万次</p></blockquote>\n<p>8月9日，他在推特称自己一觉醒来已在推特<strong>被提及了30多万次</strong>：</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/markhorton2.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-537388\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/markhorton2.jpg\" alt=\"markhorton2\" width=\"450\" height=\"154\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/markhorton2.jpg 1790w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/markhorton2-300x103.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/markhorton2-768x263.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/markhorton2-1024x351.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>还以为第三天会平息下来，早上醒来一看推特已经被提及超过30万次了。</p></blockquote>\n<p>在英国 Mark 抱怨自己第三天仍被继续被轰炸后，还是有“爱国”青年对其“误伤”：</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/markhorton4.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-537393\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/markhorton4.jpg\" alt=\"markhorton4\" width=\"450\" height=\"456\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/markhorton4.jpg 1929w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/markhorton4-296x300.jpg 296w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/markhorton4-768x778.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/markhorton4-1011x1024.jpg 1011w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/markhorton4-70x70.jpg 70w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a></p>\n<p>有中国／华人推友调侃前来“出征”的中国人民“<strong>玻璃心</strong>”，很快就被“出征”者自证了：</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/玻璃心.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-537392\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/玻璃心.jpg\" alt=\"玻璃心\" width=\"450\" height=\"205\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/玻璃心.jpg 1930w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/玻璃心-300x136.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/玻璃心-768x349.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/08/玻璃心-1024x466.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a></p>\n<p>澳洲代表团团长 Kitty Chiller 后来公开<a href=\"http://www.cnn.com/2016/08/08/sport/sun-yang-mack-horton-australia-china/\" target=\"_blank\">表示</a>，“霍顿有权表达自己的观点和不满”、“我们无意道歉”。</p>\n<p><strong>当地时间8月9日，据澳洲《先驱太阳报》网站<a href=\"http://www.heraldsun.com.au/sport/olympics-2016/mack-hortons-parents-say-theres-only-one-group-theyll-say-sorry-to/news-story/bc25a83e562eec232258adaa76723498\" target=\"_blank\">报道</a>，霍顿父亲表示需要为孙杨事件道歉，但对象不是孙杨，更不是愤怒的中国民众，而是为过去两天里因与自己儿子名字相同而遭受网络暴力的人道歉：</strong></p>\n<blockquote><p>“We probably just need to apologise to every Horton who has a name like Mack – because they have really copped a fair shellacking over the last couple of days,” Andrew Horton said.</p>\n<p>我们可能只需要向每一位姓霍顿名Mack的人道歉——在过去两天里他们被整得太惨了。</p></blockquote>\n<p>【编者注】有中国媒体对霍顿父亲的道歉内容<a href=\"http://2016.sina.com.cn/china/2016-08-10/doc-ifxutfpc4945674.shtml\" target=\"_blank\">理解有误</a>，错将“copped a fair shellacking”译成“忍受着公平的失败”。</p>\n","author":980,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,27949],"tags":[9970,24652,25322,31546,30038,30044,10268,9481,31559]}